&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate would be responsible for the assessment and treatment of a caseload of service users with mental health problems as a result of their long term physical health problems. We are a small supportive team working within Solihull Primary Care Communities. Our referrals are predominately from District Nurses, Intermediate Care and Community Falls Team. The aim of the service is to prevent admission to Acute Hospitals.&lt;/p&gt;
